print(
    "RIDGE PLOT 2: ONE CATEGORY, ALL VARIABLES SAMPLES, DIFFERENT STAR MASSES -> VARIATIONS WITH STAR MASS (VERY DIFFERENT FOR DIFFERENT CATEGORIES, NEED ANOTHER PLOT TO SHOW THAT"
